Map Name: gg_mr_grande

Version: 1.0

Created By: Paul '[MalReynolds]' Elliott

Email: whde2000@yahoo.co.uk

Dev Notes: After a long hiatus i thought i'd make another map.Initially the idea was to have a bridge and work around it. Overall time spent on it was about 12 hours across 2 days. Tried looking at different curving techniques, which i liked with mixed results and overall i think the map plays good and has alot to keep players interested.

Dev textures from FPSBanana http://www.fpsbanana.com/ by Chris528. Thanks for the textures.

Custom Textures added with Pakrat.

Spawn Points: 32
